<h1>PART 3042 CONTRACT ADMINISTRATION AND AUDIT SERVICES</h1>
<hr size="2" width="80%"><p><a href="3042.html" name="LOC_P0_0">PART 3042 CONTRACT ADMINISTRATION AND AUDIT SERVICES</a></p>

    <ul><ul><li><a href="3042.html" name="LOC_P6_226">3042.1502 Policy.</a></li>

  </ul></ul><ul><li><a href="3042.html" name="LOC_P10_1143">Subpart 3042.70 Contracting Officer's Technical Representative </a></li>

  <ul><li><a href="3042.html" name="LOC_P11_1206">3042.7000 Contract clause.</a></li></ul></ul><hr size="2" width="80%"><!-- TRANSIT - TEXTBAR --><p align="center"><a name="P0_0"></a><b>PART 3042 CONTRACT ADMINISTRATION AND AUDIT SERVICES</b></p>

<br><b>Subpart 3042.2 [Removed]</b>

<br><b>Subpart 3042.15 Contractor Performance Information</b>

<br>3042.1502 Policy.

<br><b>Subpart 3042.70 Contracting Officer's Technical Representative</b>

<br>3042.7000 Contract clause.

<p><a name="P6_226"></a><b>3042.1502 Policy.</b></p>

<p>(a) Components shall use the Contractor Performance Assessment Reporting System (CPARS) or other performance reporting system as designated by the DHS Chief Procurement Officer for evaluating contractor performance in accordance with (FAR) 48 CFR sections <font color="#0000ff" size="+0"><u><!-- TRANSIT - HYPERLINK --><!-- .../Far/FAR42.doc#b421502. --><a href="../../far2afmcfars/fardfars/Far/42.html">42.1502</a></u></font> and <font color="#0000ff" size="+0"><u><!-- TRANSIT - HYPERLINK --><!-- .../Far/FAR42.doc#b421503. --><a href="../../far2afmcfars/fardfars/Far/42.html">42.1503</a></u></font>. </p>

<p>(e) Components shall use the Construction Contractor Appraisal Support System (CCASS) module of CPARS, or other performance reporting system as designated by the DHS Chief Procurement Officer for evaluating construction contractor performance in accordance with (FAR) 48 CFR sections <font color="#0000ff" size="+0"><u><!-- TRANSIT - HYPERLINK --><!-- .\\fspih\regs$\Farsite\HSAR\Changes\Far\FAR42.doc#b421502. --><a href="http://farsite.hill.af.mil/reghtml/regs/other/hsar/FAR42.doc#b421502">42.1502</a></u></font> and <font color="#0000ff" size="+0"><u><!-- TRANSIT - HYPERLINK --><!-- .\\fspih\regs$\Farsite\HSAR\Changes\Far\FAR42.doc#b421503. --><a href="http://farsite.hill.af.mil/reghtml/regs/other/hsar/FAR42.doc#b421503">42.1503</a></u></font>. </p>

<p>(f) Components shall use the Architect-Engineer Contract Administration Support System (ACASS) module of CPARS or other performance reporting system as designated by the DHS Chief Procurement Officer for evaluating architect-engineer contractor performance in accordance with (FAR) 48 CFR sections <font color="#0000ff" size="+0"><u><!-- TRANSIT - HYPERLINK --><!-- .\\fspih\regs$\Farsite\HSAR\Changes\Far\FAR42.doc#b421502. --><a href="http://farsite.hill.af.mil/reghtml/regs/other/hsar/FAR42.doc#b421502">42.1502</a></u></font> and <font color="#0000ff" size="+0"><u><!-- TRANSIT - HYPERLINK --><!-- .\\fspih\regs$\Farsite\HSAR\Changes\Far\FAR42.doc#b421503. --><a href="http://farsite.hill.af.mil/reghtml/regs/other/hsar/FAR42.doc#b421503">42.1503</a></u></font>.</p>

<p><a name="P10_1143"></a><b>Subpart 3042.70 Contracting Officer's Technical Representative </b></p>

<p><a name="P11_1206"></a><b>3042.7000 Contract clause.</b></p>

<p>The contracting officer shall insert the clause at (HSAR) 48 CFR <font color="#0000ff" size="+0"><u><!-- TRANSIT - HYPERLINK --><!-- .3052.doc#s305224272. --><a href="3052.html">3052.242-72</a></u></font>, Contracting Officer's Technical Representative, in solicitations and contracts when it is intended that a representative will be assigned to the contract to perform functions of a technical nature.</p>
